 {"actor":"beads/witness","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-01T16:42:46Z","event_type":"updated","id":2540,"issue_id":"bd-d96s","new_value":"{\"description\":\"In hooks_migration.go lines ~189-201, detectHookMarkerState uses strings.Contains to check for hookMarkerBeginTag and hookMarkerEndTag. If a hook file has been corrupted to contain two BEGIN tags and one END tag (or two full marker blocks), the function returns hookMarkerStateValid. It should verify exactly one BEGIN and one END exist, and that BEGIN precedes END, to correctly detect corruption.\\n\\nSuggested fix: Count occurrences of each tag and verify order.\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"bd-d96s\",\"title\":\"detectHookMarkerState does not validate marker count or order\",\"description\":\"attached_molecule: bd-wisp-p1788\\nattached_formula: mol-polecat-work\\nattached_at: 2026-03-01T23:51:05Z\\ndispatched_by: mayor\\n\\nIn hooks_migration.go lines ~189-201, detectHookMarkerState uses strings.Contains to check for hookMarkerBeginTag and hookMarkerEndTag. If a hook file has been corrupted to contain two BEGIN tags and one END tag (or two full marker blocks), the function returns hookMarkerStateValid. It should verify exactly one BEGIN and one END exist, and that BEGIN precedes END, to correctly detect corruption.\\n\\nSuggested fix: Count occurrences of each tag and verify order.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"bug\",\"assignee\":\"beads/polecats/quartz\",\"owner\":\"steve.yegge@gmail.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T18:11:56Z\",\"created_by\":\"beads/polecats/jasper\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-02T00:09:35Z\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-02T00:09:35Z\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}"}
