 {"actor":"mayor","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-01T19:08:02Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":2547,"issue_id":"bd-7fsv","new_value":"{\"assignee\":\"beads/polecats/onyx\",\"status\":\"hooked\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"bd-7fsv\",\"title\":\"Hand-rolled YAML parser in multirepo.go is incorrect\",\"description\":\"In multirepo.go lines ~155-188, readTypesFromYAML implements a manual YAML parser instead of using gopkg.in/yaml.v3 (already imported in database.go in the same package). The comment says 'For simplicity, we'll parse it manually to avoid viper state issues' but the manual parser is incorrect: it does not handle multi-line YAML arrays, nested indentation, or YAML anchors/aliases. No test coverage exists for CheckMultiRepoTypes.\\n\\nSuggested fix: Use yaml.Unmarshal as database.go does. Add tests.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"bug\",\"owner\":\"steve.yegge@gmail.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-01T18:11:20Z\",\"created_by\":\"beads/polecats/jasper\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-01T18:11:20Z\"}"}
